  "future": [
    "Surface dirty tricks as actionable buttons in the Actions tab and map-side quick panel.",
    "Add stronger ship-combat integrations for rigging, boarding, morale, and cannon-adjacent play."
  ],
  "buildTips": [
    "Dexterity is your main combat stat; Charisma sharpens many class themes and makes the social side sing.",
    "Fight where movement matters: ladders, bridges, doors, rails, corners, and cover all favor you.",
    "Use Swagger Dice proactively; the class feels best when you keep pressure high rather than hoarding resources."
  ]
